page.title: 17Local Newspapers
page.content: In this area there are several local newspapers such as athe West Briton,The Falmouth Packet and The Western Mornig News.Mostly they have stories about what is happening in this area.The pictures in The West Briton are not very good,theybare all fuzzy and when I looked at the photo they had of me in "Okklahoma" that we did at school this year I could hardly recognize myself.There are two kinds of this paper,oneios just for Truro and if you want that one you have to look for the big black circle in the top corne r.
